snippet.title: Sonic Frontiers: Sonic's Birthday Event
snippet.description:
This video shows off Sonic's birthday event in Sonic Frontiers PC Steam. Sonic, Tails, Knuckles and Amy now have a festive new skin, and the Starfall Islands are also decorated with confetti, balloons and more!
Sonic Frontiers DLC Update 2 Birthday Bash 4K gameplay captured on PC.
#sonicthehedgehog #sonic #sonicfrontiers

‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒

00:00 Intro
00:07 Sonic's Birthday Skin Showcase
00:29 Rescuing Amy (Cutscene)
01:17 Kronos Island - Open Zone Gameplay
03:18 Rescuing Knuckles (Cutscene)
04:30 Ares Island - Open Zone Gameplay
06:57 Rescuing Tails (Cutscene)
08:32 Chaos Island - Open Zone Gameplay
